Comment: 1,0:00:05.94,0:00:07.94,JP-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,OP前
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.94,0:00:08.98,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.98,0:00:10.55,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,それはないかな
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.55,0:00:11.06,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ないよね
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.06,0:00:11.83,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,何でよ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.83,0:00:14.04,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,いいでしょ　グローリアス・エーンジェル号
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.04,0:00:15.63,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ビッチな感じがする
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.63,0:00:16.94,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あと　頭悪いか
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.94,0:00:18.84,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ゴージャスって言ってよ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.84,0:00:20.79,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,文句つけるんだったらて談や出して
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.79,0:00:21.60,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.60,0:00:24.11,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,じゃあ　アートマン号
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.11,0:00:25.11,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,何それ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.11,0:00:28.54,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,分かりやすく　池袋エクスプレスとかはどうかな
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.54,0:00:29.62,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そのまんまだね
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.62,0:00:32.05,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でも　早い感じ出てるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.05,0:00:34.32,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんは何かないの
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.59,0:00:37.51,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,アポジー　とか
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.51,0:00:38.56,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,何ジー
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.56,0:00:39.55,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,アポジー
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.55,0:00:43.06,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,月とか衛星が地球から一番遠ざかる地点のこと
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.16,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.22,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんかオシャレ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.22,0:00:46.97,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,いいんじゃない　アポジ号
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.97,0:00:47.61,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.50,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,お前はこれからアポジ爺だ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.57,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん　星とか宇宙とか好きだったの
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.57,0:00:53.24,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,初耳
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.12,0:00:56.82,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私じゃなくて　葉香
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.82,0:00:57.73,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.26,0:01:00.00,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,っが教えてくれた
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.00,0:01:01.60,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やっぱし意外
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.60,0:01:03.54,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんってどっちかっていうと
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.54,0:01:06.00,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,絵本とかふわふわとかそんな感じだった
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.00,0:01:09.68,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そう言えば葉香ちゃん　何で池袋に行ったんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.56,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,しかも一人でだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.56,0:01:12.90,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そうそう　それ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.90,0:01:14.66,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,私も前から気になってた
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.66,0:01:18.30,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃん　一人で何かするイメージ　全然ないもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.30,0:01:19.48,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そうそう
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.48,0:01:22.97,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そんな葉香ちゃんがたった一人で池袋へ行くってのが
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.97,0:01:24.80,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,変っていうか　不思議
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.80,0:01:26.81,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ちょっとしたミステリーだね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.81,0:01:27.76,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.76,0:01:29.93,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋って他に何かあったっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.93,0:01:33.84,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あとは　本屋とか劇場とか水族館とか
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.84,0:01:35.63,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,えっ　そんなとこ行く人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.25,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,行くイメージが全然ないね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.25,0:01:38.46,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だよね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.46,0:01:40.28,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんって輪には入ってるけど
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.89,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,自分から何かするタイプじゃなかったもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.89,0:01:44.95,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,いつも輪の中でニコニコしてた
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.95,0:01:48.10,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,なんか　私たち葉香ちゃんのこと
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.10,0:01:50.16,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,よく分かってなかったんだなって
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.65,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やだ　撫子ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.53,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,寂しいこと言わないで
Comment: 1,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.80,JP-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.68,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,地球と月が最も離れた場合
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.87,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,その距離は40万ボボボ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.01,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ああ　5分
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.20,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,短すぎるよ　毎度毎度
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.99,0:03:39.18,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,これ焼いて塩振って食べると美味しいよね
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.18,0:03:41.81,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,余ったらあとでたけのこご飯にしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.81,0:03:43.23,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ぼっちさん
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.93,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,どうしたの晶ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.65,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ぼっちさんがゲロ吐いた
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.07,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.34,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,猫とかよく吐くよ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.17,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,でも吾野出てから吐くの初めてだし
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.81,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,なんか変なもの食べた
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.67,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.04,0:04:03.55,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,どうしようぼっちさんになんかあったら
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.73,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋ついたら
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.73,0:04:07.61,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんぼっちさんに探してもらわなきゃいけないからね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.61,0:04:10.52,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんの匂いたどれるのはぼっちさんだけだし
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.52,0:04:14.10,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,だから　絶対元気でいてもらわないといけないんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.75,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ぼっちさんって幾つだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.19,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うん　ぼっちさんって
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.49,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,私らが子供の頃からずっとぼっちさんじゃなかったっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.02,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,てことは13、14歳くらい
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うわっもう　おじいちゃん犬じゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.53,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,最悪
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.03,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,人が小雪婆の年のこと言ったときは
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.17,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,そんなこと言うなって怒ったくせに
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.17,0:04:31.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あん時とは違うでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.68,0:04:32.92,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,同じだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.92,0:04:37.13,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ぼっちさんが死んじゃったら　死んじゃうんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.87,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶さ　あのさ…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.97,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大丈夫　大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.31,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,たぶん　大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.10,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん全然説得力ないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.69,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,心配じゃないの
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.69,0:04:51.22,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ぼっちさん連れてきたのは静留ちゃんなのに
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.37,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,えっ　待って
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.50,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私が無理やり乗せたんじゃないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.24,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼっちさんがついてきたんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.93,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,またそれ言う
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.24,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,私たちが今ここにいること
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.37,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんに無理やりじゃないでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.27,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ついてきたんでしょって言われたら
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.32,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,その通りだと思うけど冷たいって思うよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.82,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,これ　前にも言ったと思うけど
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.82,0:05:11.50,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,えっと
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.64,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,あのね　静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.92,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんはなんで池袋に行ったの
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.92,0:05:16.53,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.47,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんは何か知ってるんじゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.47,0:05:19.96,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんで今それ聞くの
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.20,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,今　聞いちゃ駄目なの
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.19,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,何で
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.14,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,駄目じゃないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.86,0:05:28.75,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喧嘩した
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.18,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やっぱり
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.07,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.59,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あんまし言いたくない
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.10,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,言いたくない
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.54,0:05:41.34,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんは葉香ちゃんに　何か言ったかしたんだね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.47,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,えっ　葉香ちゃんが怒ったの
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.69,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんが泣なって想像できない
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.69,0:05:48.22,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,本当はよく分かんない
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.64,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,分かんないって
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.92,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,何かしたんだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.37,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ただ「そか」って言われただけ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.33,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,えへ　意外
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.68,0:05:57.99,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,そうかな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.14,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そうだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.64,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,えへ　何
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.64,0:06:02.65,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,宇宙って　この宇宙でしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.70,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香ってそんなこと考えてたんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.52,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,全然知らなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.52,0:06:08.49,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そういうのって何ていうの
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.36,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あ　そうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.04,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,天文学だ天文学
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.89,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,まあ　私がやりたいのは
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.10,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,これからの惑星探査衛星とか
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.76,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,宇宙ステーションの誘導や
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.35,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,制御技術の開発とシス…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.99,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,どうやって　そういう仕事する人になるの
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.99,0:06:21.85,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.85,0:06:25.23,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,大学行って　勉強して　論文とか書いて
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.16,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,それから
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.16,0:06:29.11,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,研究機関の採用があったら応募
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.94,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,応募　それだけ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.48,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,うん　まあ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.98,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.96,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,何かよく分かんないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.47,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,むっちゃ難しいんじゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.44,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,知ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.21,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,けど　でも…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.61,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香すごいね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.71,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,すごくないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.91,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,いや　でも
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.21,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,宇宙の　衛星の
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.21,0:06:56.34,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そういうのになりたいって　まず思わないもん
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.01,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,思いつく気もしないって感じ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.86,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でもさ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.55,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,リアルに考えて　どうなんだろうね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.55,0:07:03.72,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,リアルって
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.17,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そういうの
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.47,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,そういうの
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.47,0:07:09.27,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,だって　私ら普通の人間でしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.36,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そういうのって
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.49,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんかもっと特別な人がやることなんじゃないのかなって
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.75,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ああ　葉香のこと別に馬鹿にしてるんじゃないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.75,0:07:21.31,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でも　なんかものすごい遠いこと話されてる気がして
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.31,0:07:22.33,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,遠いかな
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.82,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,遠いよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.82,0:07:26.77,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野のから星とか宇宙とか銀河系って
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.77,0:07:27.93,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,無理　無理　無理
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.93,0:07:30.43,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あんまり大きいこと言うと恥ずかしいっていうか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.43,0:07:33.45,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ある程度　現実と折り合いつけていくもんじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.47,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,無理　無理
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.26,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,もっと普通でいいじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.59,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,普通にしかなれないし
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.59,0:07:40.26,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,てゆか　あんまし特別とか考えなくてよくない
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.28,0:07:44.70,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香もさ　そういうこと考えるのはいいことだと思うけど
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.31,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,できなかった時　辛いし
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.85,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ていうか無理だよね　葉香には
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.22,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,まあ　私もか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.66,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私たちってことだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.75,0:07:54.80,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,えっ　何
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.58,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,何って
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.68,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,いきなり黙ったから
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.25,0:07:59.45,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんか変なこと言った
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.08,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,別に
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.92,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,そうかと思っただけ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.44,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そうかって何
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.46,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私が言ったこと気に入らないんだったら
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.75,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,言ってくれればいいでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.41,0:08:09.63,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,人それぞれだし
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.31,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,すっごい突き放した言い方するね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.22,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,冷たくない
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.66,0:08:16.39,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私は間違ったこと言ってないつもりだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.47,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,そうなんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.31,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,静留ってそういう人なんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.94,0:08:24.63,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,はあ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.62,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,何だよ　そういう人って
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.62,0:08:28.69,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香こそそういう人だったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.24,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,そうだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.99,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,私はこういうやつだから
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.77,0:08:34.61,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.98,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,何　ごめんって
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.54,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,知らないからねもう　葉香のことなんか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.28,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,私は静留ちゃんが悪いと思うよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.28,0:08:47.89,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,いきなり駄目出しされたらやっぱりへこむしむかつくよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.89,0:08:50.67,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好きなことけなされたら余計ね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.67,0:08:51.48,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,わかって…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.48,0:08:55.34,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんだって分かってるよ　ひどいこと言ったって
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.77,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ひどいことかな
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.65,0:09:00.90,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そんなにひどいこと言ったかな
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.90,0:09:04.83,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だって　葉香ちゃんはだから1人で池袋に行っちゃったんでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.65,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,でも　なんで池袋
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.42,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確かに　なんでだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.45,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ねえ　なんで池袋
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.47,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,わかんない
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.47,0:09:15.74,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,でも　葉香ちゃんが喧嘩したせいで吾野を飛び出したってのも
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.41,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,これはたぶん　事実だよね
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.41,0:09:20.94,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,たとえ静留ちゃんが悪いこと言ったつもりがなくても
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.94,0:09:24.99,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんが傷ついたんなら　それは悪いことなんじゃないの
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.14,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ていうかさ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.14,0:09:29.76,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんは葉香ちゃんに会って　謝りたいんだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.76,0:09:30.98,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.75,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香だっていきなり出てったのはひどくない
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.62,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,まあ　どっちもちょっとずつ悪いよね
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.01,0:09:42.70,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,二人のことは二人のことだから　何とも言えないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.70,0:09:46.68,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,私は静留ちゃんがこのこと今まで話してくれなかったのが悲しい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.04,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あ　それ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.04,0:09:48.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.83,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんで話してくれなかったのかーって気がする
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.77,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,やましさ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.99,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,別に
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.99,0:09:56.57,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,みんなを無理やり引きずり出したわけじゃないし
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.18,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そういう言い方はないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.40,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,8,,{\an8}ひどい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.56,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,じゃないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.56,0:10:03.16,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんは私たちが勝手についてきたと思ってるの
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.91,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,みんなで池袋に行きたいと思ってたけど
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.82,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんはそうじゃなかったってこと
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.82,0:10:11.69,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私は　池袋に行きたかっただけだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.87,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん一人でってこと
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.64,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そうかもね
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.81,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え　何それ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.22,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,超今更発言
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.35,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　ごめん　そうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.87,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,やっぱ私一人の方がいいかも
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.55,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,てかお互いそうだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.65,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん何すんの
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.65,0:10:28.60,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,出てく
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.36,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一人で行く
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.36,0:10:29.87,JP-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.87,0:10:30.60,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.63,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,待ってよそんな急に
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.11,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,もう暗いのに
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.27,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.27,0:10:37.50,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃん止めて
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.36,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんが行っちゃう
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.45,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ちょっと冷静になった方がいいかも
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.41,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.89,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,行かせていいの
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.89,0:10:47.37,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,無理やり引き戻した方がいい
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.69,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,それは
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.27,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,頭冷やそう
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.62,0:10:51.76,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,私たちも
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.02,0:10:57.12,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ぼっちさん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.12,0:10:59.01,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんとこ行くの
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.62,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,えっ　行っちゃヤダ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.57,0:11:05.45,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ぼっちさんなら　静留ちゃんのこと何とかしてくれるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.90,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.26,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼっちさんか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.77,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,向こうに戻りなよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.20,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,また無理やり連れてきたとか言われる
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.11,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,行ってないか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.27,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でもほんといいのに
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.13,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼっちさんの意思だからね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.13,0:11:28.13,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私は冷たいからね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.15,0:11:31.65,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ご飯食べよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.52,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,もうさ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.52,0:11:35.21,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃんはどうしてそんな落ち着いてられんの
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.19,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.19,0:11:39.71,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,その質問八つ当たりが目的なんだったら私は答えないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.05,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.05,0:11:46.97,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,八つ当たりも65%くらいあったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.24,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,35%はほんとに聞きたいです
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.24,0:11:50.60,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,あのね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.60,0:11:54.04,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,池袋に行くには線路自体に行くしかないでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.15,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そんで線路は一本しかないし
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.62,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,それを辿っていけば絶対静留ちゃんに追いつくってこと
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.62,0:12:00.37,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あ　そっか
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.06,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.84,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,今一瞬怖かったよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.45,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,え　ほんと
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.46,0:12:10.45,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ご飯食べて　機嫌直そ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.41,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,いただきます
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.76,0:12:15.75,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あのさ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.42,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やっぱこのアポジーはさ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.24,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんの電車だと思うな
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.92,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ペリジーでもよかったんだもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.92,0:12:22.98,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,何ジー
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.98,0:12:23.84,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ペリジー
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.04,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,地球と月が一番離れてるとこがアポジーで
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.04,0:12:28.52,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,近いとこがペリジー
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.59,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんと葉香ちゃんの距離
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.60,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,分かんないけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.01,0:12:34.67,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,でも　これから会いに行こうってのに
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.67,0:12:35.94,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,近い名前じゃなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.39,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,遠い名前をつけるのってなんかちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.11,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんかちょっとだね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.87,0:12:41.98,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,おかわりたん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.16,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,え　はやっ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.83,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うぇい　早いものがちん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.69,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,デブるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.69,0:12:46.40,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.91,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そういう意地悪言わないの
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.61,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大回りやだな
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.43,0:13:00.17,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,近道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.37,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,次は清瀬か
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.42,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,すぐ見つかるよね
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.78,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ちょっとでも池袋に急がないとね
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.49,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,今日はここに泊まって
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.59,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,明日朝になったら出発しよっか
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.59,0:13:15.27,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あんまりすぐ静留ちゃんに追いついちゃうと
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.82,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんか恥ずかしいもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.82,0:13:17.85,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,お互いね
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.95,0:13:21.85,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,私は静留ちゃんを許すよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.33,0:13:23.59,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,何言ってんの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.42,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だって友達だもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.41,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,てことは
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.41,0:13:29.39,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,許さなかった葉香ちゃんは友達じゃなかったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.08,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え　ええ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.08,0:13:31.87,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,違うよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.26,0:13:35.41,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,喧嘩したり許したりするのも含めて友達だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.70,0:13:39.03,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,でも　許さなかったら関係は途絶えるよね
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.70,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,それでも友達かな
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.47,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,もう一生会えなくても
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.57,0:13:44.94,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やめやめ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.94,0:13:48.14,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,寝る前に難しいこと考えてると悪い夢見る
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.21,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,おかしいなぁ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.21,0:13:53.07,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,1時間くらいで越えられるはずだったのに
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.62,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,3時間も登ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.47,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,こんなにかかるはずだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.47,0:13:57.59,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,違うよね
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.42,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼっちさん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.42,0:14:00.91,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,リアクションは
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.91,0:14:03.98,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一人で喋ってる怖い人じゃん私
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.08,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,馬鹿だな
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.98,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんでこんな馬鹿なんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.38,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,戻った方がいい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.79,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,戻るべき
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.77,0:14:21.95,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,決めた
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.95,0:14:22.71,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,戻ろう
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.92,0:14:25.56,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.00,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,どっちだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.00,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,迷った時は下るんじゃなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.67,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,登るっていうのが鉄則だし
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.67,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼっちさん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.88,0:14:49.88,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんだろ　変な匂い
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.73,0:14:54.88,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なえぼっち　え
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.88,0:14:55.79,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.81,0:14:57.16,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ポ…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.25,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,まじが
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.83,0:15:11.21,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼっちさん
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.97,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あんたらどこのまんよ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.60,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,清瀬のまんか
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.23,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野柔術なめんなよ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.76,0:15:27.85,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ぼっちさん
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.41,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,この　まじいけ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.96,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,煩い
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.21,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,おやめ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.59,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,久しぶりだ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.98,0:15:58.39,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,連れていこう
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.22,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,えええ　待ってちょっとあ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.51,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,煩いよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.68,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,いないね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.81,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,どっかで見落としちゃったかな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.16,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,通り過ぎちゃったとか
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.69,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,でも相当ゆっくり来たよね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.69,0:16:19.41,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,きた
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.87,0:16:23.16,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃん　静留ちゃんは線路外れたんじゃない?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.50,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,外れたとしたら　どこから外れたんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.39,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,どこだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.92,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,私が聞いてんだってば
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,私だってわかんないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.42,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,戻ったほうがいいのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.42,0:16:32.97,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.01,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,じゃあ進む
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.67,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,朝から結構来たのに
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.67,0:16:38.35,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だって　撫子ちゃんが落ち着こうって言ったでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.13,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そんで落ち着いた静留ちゃんが戻ってきてたら
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.13,0:16:41.81,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,どこに
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.81,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だから　出てった元の場所に
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.90,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,出てって戻ってくるってある
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.38,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あるかもしれないじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.92,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,でも静留ちゃんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.92,0:16:49.53,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.80,0:16:53.45,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんがちゃんと線路行ってるかどうかわかんないしね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.15,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,でも　道路は線路より危険だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.66,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だよねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.84,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,でも静留ちゃんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.32,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あれ　あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.32,0:17:03.91,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.67,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,黙って
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.47,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,なんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.19,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,これ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.78,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,黒豹キャラバン
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.17,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,猫兄さん達だ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.54,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,名前は
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.54,0:17:22.13,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,千倉静留
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.13,0:17:23.58,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野高校2年
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.72,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吾野高ね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.72,0:17:26.73,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,私は黒木美都
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.35,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,黒木さんでいいよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.35,0:17:31.23,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,黒木さんはゾンビですよね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.13,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,なんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.30,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あ　いや
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.30,0:17:37.17,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,黒木さんだけ喋れるのって何でだろうって思って
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.56,0:17:43.33,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,私が喋れるのはね　ゾンビの女王だからさ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.88,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ゾンビの女王
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.58,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,電車で池袋に
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.38,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,また無茶なことを
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.48,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ねえ　猫兄さん
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.96,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,他になんか情報ないの
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.33,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,最新の池袋情報
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.33,0:17:57.49,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,最新って言っても　ずいぶん前の話になるからな
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.96,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,それに聞いた話だし
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.18,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,全然大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.65,0:18:04.44,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,まあ　吾野も相当変だけど　池袋はそれ以上だな
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.73,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,引き延ばされて看板にされたり
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.73,0:18:08.62,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,茶碗蒸しにされて蒸されたりする
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.24,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.04,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,意味わかんないんですけど
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.15,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,だろうな
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.15,0:18:12.87,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.87,0:18:17.49,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,この世界って西部池袋線しか存在しないって本当なんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.49,0:18:21.15,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,自分で詳しく調べたわけじゃないから断言はできないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.15,0:18:23.38,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,その可能性は否定できないね
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.38,0:18:26.87,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,他の遠征を探している人たちの話を聞くと特にね
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.87,0:18:30.07,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,この後またぐるっといろいろ回るんですよね
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.21,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,うん　ああ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.45,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,もしどこかの集落でも　 キャラバンの途中でも
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.45,0:18:37.38,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんを見つけられたらいつでも戻ってきて
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.29,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,待ってるって伝えてください
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.29,0:18:42.14,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,それはいいけど　見つかるかな
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.61,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え　ちょっとそんな頼りなさげなことを
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.61,0:18:47.22,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,みんなもいろいろ見てきてるとは思うけど
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.22,0:18:50.97,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,7Gで様変わりしたこの世界はとてつもなく広いからね
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.74,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,たった一人の人間と会えるかどうか
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.33,0:18:58.48,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,池袋も難関だけど　この辺りも不穏な気配がある
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.48,0:19:00.16,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,君らも早く移動した方がいい
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.46,0:19:01.83,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,何があるんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.08,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,ゾンビだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.08,0:19:05.11,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あの死体の　黄泉がえりの
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.40,0:19:08.45,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ちょうど渡りゾンビの目撃情報が入ってきたとこだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.42,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,渡りゾンビ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.92,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,ゾンビはこれで繊細なのさ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.94,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,暑けりゃ腐るし　寒けりゃ凍って折れる
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.13,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,雨が降ればドロドロになるし
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.20,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,かといって乾燥しすぎも良くない
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.60,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そうですね
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.60,0:19:25.14,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,だからちょうどいい気候と土地を探して
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.14,0:19:27.05,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,始終移動してるってわけだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.05,0:19:28.32,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.11,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,私はその羅針盤
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.11,0:19:33.07,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,女王だから　こいつらを導く義務がある
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.85,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そうだったんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.52,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,元気がないね
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.87,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,腹でも減ったかい
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.87,0:19:40.41,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え　あ　はい　そうですね
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.41,0:19:42.58,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,とりま　なんか一本食わせてやんな
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.87,0:19:44.05,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一本
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.33,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え　ぽ　ぽんて
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.61,0:19:47.70,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,食いな
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.18,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,遠慮はいらないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.29,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え　いえ　あの
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.61,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,こういうビーフジャーキー的なの
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.61,0:19:54.57,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,歯の隙間に挟まるんで避けてるんです
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.81,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,あ　そう
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.81,0:19:56.38,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,そっちは
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.66,0:19:57.71,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,食うか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.68,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,要らないでさえ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.33,0:20:07.41,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,やっぱり　干し肉みたいな味なんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.41,0:20:08.55,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,知らない
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.46,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,食べたことがないんでね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.46,0:20:10.93,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.93,0:20:12.70,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,あたしは女王だから
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.70,0:20:14.82,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,特別なものを食べるのさ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.56,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,一緒に行けなくて悪いね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.43,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,こっちも仕事があるんでね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.99,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,いえ　そんな全然
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.03,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,気をつけて
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.16,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,ゾンビに会ったら
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.19,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,とにもかくにも動かないのが一番だ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.57,0:20:29.03,JP-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,さっき言った対策は　あくまで説の一つだから
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.04,JP-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,ゾンビ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.04,0:20:32.85,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あれでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.54,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,目玉が垂れてたり　腐ってたり
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.14,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,脳みそ吸ったり　人噛んだり
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.14,0:20:37.21,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,だいたい合ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.48,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ゾンビに噛まれたらゾンビになる
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.34,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,だいたいなる
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.11,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,どうしよう　しずるちゃんがゾンビになってたら
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.11,0:20:45.27,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,最近は割と賢かったり
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.27,0:20:48.35,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,生きてた頃の人格あるゾンビもいるとかいないとか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.35,0:20:49.57,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,襲ってこない
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.57,0:20:50.34,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,襲う
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.22,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あ　猫兄さん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.67,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,猫兄さんについて行った方が良くない
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.46,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,今だったらまだ追いつけるかも
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.26,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,って　静留ちゃんは
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.15,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんがゾンビになってたら
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.86,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,猫兄さんといる方がいいじゃん　安全じゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.86,0:21:06.39,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃんは静留ちゃんがゾンビになってたら
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.39,0:21:07.74,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,もう一緒にいられない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.53,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,友達じゃないって言いたいの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.37,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,友達だけどゾンビだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.17,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ゾンビだけど友達じゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.94,0:21:17.00,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ゾンビでも友達だよ　たぶん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.30,0:21:19.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あのさ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.68,0:21:22.21,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ひどい男と付き合ってる女の人が
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.63,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ギャンブルさえなけりゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.22,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,お酒さえ飲まなけれりゃいい人なんですって言って
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.82,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,それに対して　お酒飲むから
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.82,0:21:31.81,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,それは悪い人なんですってみんなアドバイスするじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.93,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,これってそういうこと
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.67,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.09,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,違う気がする
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.09,0:21:39.65,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,むしろ逆かも
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.36,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,こんなにだらしないのに好き
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.80,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,こんなにわがままだけど許すとか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.80,0:21:47.92,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,こうんなにゾンビだけど　友達みたいな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.32,0:21:52.08,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんにあんなにひどいこと言われたけど友達って
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.16,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃん思ってるかな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.30,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,思ってるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.83,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,絶対思ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.44,0:22:01.33,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんを葉香ちゃんに会わせなと
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.33,0:22:02.34,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うん
Comment: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:07.94,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,OP前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:08.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:10.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这感觉不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:11.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,确实不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:11.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,为啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:14.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我感觉很好「光荣天使号」列车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:15.63,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感觉像是泼妇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:16.94,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,而且 你也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:18.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我只是想说很华丽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:20.79,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要抱怨你也说一个呗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:21.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:24.11,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那就「真我号」列车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:25.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这啥鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:28.54,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不如用浅显易懂的「池袋特快号」怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:29.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这也差不了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:32.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 快的感觉太明显了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:34.32,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留你有什么好点子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:37.51,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「远地点号」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:38.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啥G
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:39.55,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,Apogee
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:43.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,月球或其它卫星 在绕地飞行时与地球最远的距离点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感觉好时尚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:46.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不也挺好的 远地点号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:47.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你现在就是「阿波爷爷」啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.57,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留是喜欢星空和宇宙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:53.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,首闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:56.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是我 是葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:57.73,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:00.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:01.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,果然好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:03.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香她无论到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:06.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感觉都会拿着绘本涂涂抹抹的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:09.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说起来葉香她 为什么会去池袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.56,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且还是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:12.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,对对 就这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:14.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我之前也是很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:18.30,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香一个人独自做什么事的印象 我是完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:19.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:22.97,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这样的葉香竟然一个人前往池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:24.80,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不仅奇怪 还不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:26.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,而且还带有一丝神秘感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:27.76,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:29.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋那还有啥特色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:33.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,还有就是 书店剧场水族馆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:35.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 她是会去那里的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.25,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感觉她根本不会去那些地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:38.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:40.28,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香虽然从小就和她在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.89,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但她也不是自力更生的类型呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:44.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,一直都在人面前笑眯眯的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:48.10,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感觉 我们对葉香的了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:50.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,并不知道很多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,别这样 抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.53,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要说让人寂寞的话呀
Comment: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.80,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,地球和月球相距最远的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.87,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,两者之间的距离有四十万 吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.01,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 五分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.20,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,时间太短了 每次都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:39.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这个烤熟以后撒上盐会很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:41.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,剩下的等会还能用来做竹笋饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:43.23,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么了呢小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,波奇它呕吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.34,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要是猫的话经常性呕吐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是从吾野离开后这是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吃了什么奇怪的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:03.55,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要是波奇出了事该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,到了池袋以后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:07.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,还得让波奇来帮忙找葉香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:10.52,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,能够追踪到葉香气味的只有波奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:14.10,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,所以 绝对要你平平安安的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.75,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇它现在多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯 波奇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,在我们小时候就一直和波奇一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也就是说有十三四岁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇敲 都成老爷爷犬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.53,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是谁提到小雪奶奶年龄的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这种话一说就生气了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:31.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这和那时不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:32.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:37.13,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要是波奇死了的话 我心也就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没事的 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大概没啥问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留完全没啥说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.69,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你不担心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:51.22,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,带上波奇的明明是静留你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 等会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我没有强迫它跟我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是波奇它自己跟来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,还说这话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.24,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们现在能在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,虽然并不是静留你强迫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.27,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但你要说我们只是跟着你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.32,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就算是对的也不近人情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.82,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这些 我之前也有说到过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:11.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.64,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,听我说 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.92,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香她到底为什么会去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:16.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.47,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留你肯定知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:19.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么要现在问我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.20,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,现在问不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:28.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.07,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我不想说太多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:41.34,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留对葉香 说了或是做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 葉香她生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香哭的样子完全无法想象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:48.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,实际上我也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.64,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.92,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你肯定做了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就只是说了一句「是吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸嘿 好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:57.99,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸嘿 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:02.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,宇宙 就是我们所在的宇宙对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香竟然是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.52,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我完全不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:08.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这个该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.04,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,天文学 是天文学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.89,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不过 我想做的事情是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.10,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,研制未来的行星探测卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.76,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,规划宇宙空间站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.35,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,以及控制技术的开发系…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么样 才能成为做成这些事的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:21.85,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:25.23,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,上大学 努力学习 写论文什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.16,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那之后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:29.11,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,有机会再申请研究机构的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,申请 就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.48,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,嗯 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然我不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这难道不是困难重重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.44,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.21,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.71,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我并不厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.21,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,宇宙 卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:56.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这些要高攀成就的 我从未放在心上想过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或许是我想都不敢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,现实地考虑一下 自己会成为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:03.72,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,现实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.47,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,哪些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:09.27,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毕竟 我只是个普通人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,难道不是非常特别的人才做得到的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 我不是瞧不起葉香你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:21.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 感觉你说的这些遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:22.33,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,遥不可及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:26.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,从吾野去到星辰、宇宙、银河系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:27.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:30.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,牛皮吹太大了也会不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:33.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,必须要在某种程度上接受现实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么不正常一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,都不过平凡的人罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:40.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再说了 真不需要考虑自己到底有多特别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:44.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香也是 你能够有伟大的想法很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但做不到的时候会很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再说了葉香你 不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:54.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.58,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,什么怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,突然你变得沉默了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:07:59.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我说了奇怪的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.08,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.92,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我想原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这样是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你要是不喜欢我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,直接说出来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:09.63,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,人人都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,突然这么大胆发言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不冷淡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:16.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我不认为自己有什么是说错了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.47,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.31,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,原来静留你是这样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:24.63,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.62,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么是这样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:28.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香你也是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.24,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.99,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:34.61,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说什么抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我根本对葉香你一无所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.28,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我认为是静留的错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:47.89,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,突然被人说不行 内心肯定会沮丧生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:50.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,「贬低他人喜爱之事多此一举」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:51.48,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:55.34,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留都已经明白了 自己说了很过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,很过分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:00.90,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我说的话真的很过分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:04.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,可是 这很可能是葉香一个人去池袋的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 为什么去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,呐 为什么去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:15.74,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 葉香是因为你和她吵架才离开吾野的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这大概是事实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:20.94,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就算静留说的并不是什么坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:24.99,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但伤害到了葉香 难道不是坏事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:29.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,静留想要再见到葉香 当面向她道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:30.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香她一个人就润了 难道不过分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嘛 两边都是刺儿头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:42.70,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你们两人的事自己解决 旁人说不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:46.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但我很失望静留直到现在才告诉我们这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:48.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,就是「为什么一直瞒着我们」的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.77,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,内疚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:56.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我又没强行把所有人都扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.18,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不准这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.56,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:03.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留你是不是觉得我们就是你的跟屁虫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家都想要去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.82,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而静留你是不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:11.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我只是 想去池袋而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.87,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你自己一个人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或许就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.22,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,回答太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 抱歉 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,果然还是我自己一个人更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再说了「我们」也差不了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:28.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,离开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我自己走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:29.87,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:30.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等会啊这么着急
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.11,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,已经天黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:37.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,抚子快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留她要走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稍微冷静一下或许更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,让她自己走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:47.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,迫使她回来更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.27,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,头脑冷静下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:51.76,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:57.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:59.01,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你要和静留一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 别跟她走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:05.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,如果是波奇 静留应该会做点什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,回到那边去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不然又会被说你是被我强迫带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.11,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.27,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但确实还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.13,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这可是波奇你自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:28.13,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我不近人情的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:31.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.52,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:35.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,抚子你为什么能这么冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:39.71,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果你质问的目的只是拿我出气 我不会回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.05,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:46.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,迁怒占比百分之六十五
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,剩下百分之三十五真的想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:50.60,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:54.04,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,去往池袋的唯一途径就是铁路线本身 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.15,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而这条线路只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.62,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果沿着这条线路走 肯定能追上静留的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:00.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,刚刚一瞬间好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,诶 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:10.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,吃晚饭吧 不计前嫌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.41,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:15.75,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,果然这台「远地点号」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,应该是静留的列车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,「近地点号」其实也不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:22.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么G
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:23.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,Perigee
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.04,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,地球离月球最远的距离叫远地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:28.52,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,最近的距离就叫近地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留和葉香之间的距离吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:34.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 我们正准备去见她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:35.94,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是取近的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,而是取远的名字感觉有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实有点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:41.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,耶 先到先得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,会胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:46.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不要说得这么难听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不想绕大圈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:00.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抄近道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,下站是清濑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.42,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,很快就能见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,必须要抓紧时间赶到池袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.49,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,今天就在呆在这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,明天早上再出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:15.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那么快就赶上静留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,总感觉怪不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:17.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:21.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我会原谅静留的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:23.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,毕竟我们是朋友呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:29.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,没有原谅她的葉香就不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:31.87,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:35.41,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,朋友是能容纳争吵与原谅的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:39.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 要不原谅的话关系就此断绝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这也算是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.47,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,明明再也不会相见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:44.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快停快停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:48.14,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,睡前搞哲学 噩梦找你来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.21,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:53.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,明明一个小时左右就能过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.62,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,结果三小时都在爬坡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的要花这么多时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:57.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,肯定不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.42,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:00.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,反应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:03.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我一个人自言自语很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么我会这么笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,回去更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.79,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,应该回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:21.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:22.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:25.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,往哪儿走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,迷路的时候不要往低处走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,往高处攀登是铁律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:49.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么鬼 奇怪的味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:54.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,呐波奇 诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:55.79,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:57.16,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:11.21,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你们从哪儿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,清濑来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.23,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别小看吾野柔术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:27.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这鬼 给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.21,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.59,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:58.39,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,带她来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸欸欸 等一会儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.51,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是不是哪里错过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,或者是走过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但我们走得相当慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:19.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:23.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子 静留她是不是「出轨」了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,既然出轨了 是从哪里出轨的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.39,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,从哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我在问你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,回去或许更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:32.97,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那继续前进吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,明明早上就到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:38.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,毕竟 抚子说了要冷静一下对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.13,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,然后冷静下来的静留又回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:41.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,回哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,都说了 出发时离开的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.90,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,都离开了还会回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,还是有可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但她可是静留啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:49.53,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:53.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留她到底有没有沿着铁轨走我们并不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.15,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是 道路比铁轨更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但她可是静留啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊嘞 啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:03.91,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.67,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.47,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.78,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,黑豹商队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是猫兄他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.54,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你叫啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:22.13,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,千仓静留
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:23.58,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野高中二年级
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.72,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吾野高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:26.73,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我叫黑木美都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.35,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,叫我黑木小姐就行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:31.23,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,黑木小姐是僵尸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.13,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,为啥这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:37.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我在想为什么只有黑木小姐能够说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:43.33,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我能说话 因为俺是僵尸女王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,僵尸女王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.58,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,搭列车去池袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.38,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,又在搞事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,对了 猫兄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有没有其它的情报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,最新的池袋情报
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:57.49,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,虽说是最新的 但都是很久之前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.96,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,而且我也是听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:04.44,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,嘛 吾野虽说很奇怪 但池袋比它更甚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.73,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,东西都拉长延伸成了广告牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:08.62,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,或者都被蒸成了鸡蛋羹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咱听不懂一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.15,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:12.87,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:17.49,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这个世界真的只存在西部池袋线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:21.15,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,我自己没有详细调查过 不能肯定回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:23.38,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,但并不否认这种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:26.87,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,特别是在听过那些远征之人的话以后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:30.07,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这之后还会再转好几个圈的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.21,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,嗯 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果在某个村落 或者是在商队途中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:37.38,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,找到静留以后 请转告她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,无论何时回来 我们都会等着她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:42.14,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,这倒是没问题 不过能找到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 怎么说这么靠不住的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:47.22,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,我想你们大家见过了很多的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:50.97,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,因为7G改变了这个世界 所以世界变得非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.74,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,见一个人如同大海捞针
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:58.48,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,虽然到池袋也是难关 但这边也有不稳定的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:00.16,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,建议你们也尽早行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:01.83,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.08,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:05.11,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是尸体吗「黄泉路」那部电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:08.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我们刚刚收到了僵尸迁徙的目击情报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,迁徙僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.92,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,僵尸对这点是很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.94,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,天热腐烂 寒冷冻坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.13,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,降雨的话又湿的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.20,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,但要是太干燥也不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:25.14,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,所以我们要寻找适合的气候与土地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:27.05,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,一直都在迁徙的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:28.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.11,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我就是它们的罗盘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:33.07,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,因为是女王 有义务领导它们这些僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,原来如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.52,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你没啥精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.87,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,肚子饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:40.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 啊 确实 有点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:42.58,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,多莉马 给她吃一根什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:44.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一根
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 根 一根是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:47.70,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.18,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 不用 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这种类似牛肉干的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:54.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,容易塞牙就避免食用它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.81,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:56.38,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:57.71,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.68,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,也不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:07.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,果然 那味道是像肉干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:08.55,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.46,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我又没有吃过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:10.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:12.70,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我可是女王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:14.82,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,当然要吃点特别的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.56,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,不能和你们一起走抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.43,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,我们这还有工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.99,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,没事 我们不介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.03,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,要小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.16,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,要是见到僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.19,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,无论如何按兵不动才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:29.03,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,刚刚说的对策 是恶魔理论之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.04,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:32.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,眼球垂落 身体腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.14,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吸食大脑 啃咬人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:37.21,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,大概符合的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,被僵尸咬了后会变成僵尸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,大概是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么办啊 静留要是变成僵尸咋办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:45.27,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,最近它们变得很聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:48.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感觉像是有活人格的僵尸存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:49.57,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不会袭击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:50.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 猫兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.67,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,跟着猫兄不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,现在去追还能赶得上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.26,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等 静留呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留她变成僵尸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,在猫兄那更好 更安全啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:06.39,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实是不是想说 要是静留变成了僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:07.74,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就不能在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.53,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就再也不是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,虽然是朋友 可她是僵尸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是僵尸但「更是朋友」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:17.00,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就算成僵尸了也还是朋友 大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:19.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:22.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,一个渣男和一个女人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,他既不赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,也不喝酒 她却说他是个好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,于此相对 饮酒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:31.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,就是大家口中的所谓「坏人」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这就是 那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.67,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稍微有点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.09,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感觉不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:39.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不如说正好反了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.36,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这么邋遢的也能喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.80,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这么任性的也能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:47.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,虽然是这么个僵尸 还是朋友这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:52.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留说了那么过分的话 但还是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香会这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.30,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,肯定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.83,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,绝对会的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:01.33,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,一定要带静留去见葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:02.34,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯
